- Top 1 community with the greatest impact on Xociety, delivering more than 1100 codes, maintaining daily activities on the discord of more than 200 people playing simultaneously (every day of the test) and more than 900 active players on every day of the test.

- We are not even talking in terms of impressions generated during the campaigns, as we only achieved extremely high numbers in terms of real views.

